《'''饥饿的心'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Hungry Hearts'''''}}）是一部2014年[[萨维里奥·康斯坦佐|萨维里奥·康斯坦佐]]执导的[[意大利|意大利]]剧情片，入围[[第71届威尼斯影展|第71届威尼斯影展]]主竞赛单元<ref name="Venice">{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/71st-festival/line-up/off-sel/venezia71/ |title=International competition of feature films |accessdate=24 July 2014 |work=Venice |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006083927/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/71st-festival/line-up/off-sel/venezia71/ |archivedate=2014-10-06}}</ref><ref name="Deadline">{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/07/venice-film-festival-lineup-2014-movie-list/ |title=Venice Film Festival Lineup Announced |accessdate=24 July 2014 |work=Deadline |archive-date=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728233935/http://www.deadline.com/2014/07/venice-film-festival-lineup-2014-movie-list/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，来自[[美国|美国]]的男演员[[亚当·德赖弗|亚当·德赖弗]]和意大利的女演员[[阿尔芭·罗尔瓦赫尔|阿尔芭·罗尔瓦赫尔]]分别赢得最佳男演员和最佳女演员奖<ref >{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/14/0907/02/A5GO9IMG00031H2L.html |language= |title=《寒枝雀静》擒威尼斯金狮 《闯入者》颗粒无收 |publisher=网易娱乐 |date=2014-09-07 |accessdate= |archive-date=2014-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140907083009/http://ent.163.com/14/0907/02/A5GO9IMG00031H2L.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它也是2014年[[多伦多影展|多伦多影展]]特别展映作品<ref name="Indiewire">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/tiff-toronto-intl-film-festival-gala-special-presentations-1201266480/ |title=Toronto Film Festival Lineup |accessdate=22 July 2014 |work=Variety |archive-date=2015-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151019092814/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/tiff-toronto-intl-film-festival-gala-special-presentations-1201266480/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 剧情 ==
意大利女孩米娜和美国男孩朱迪在[[纽约|纽约]]偶遇热恋，之后结婚生子。然而米娜为了孩子的健康成长所采取的极端做法却带来了悲剧结局。

